Our Board of Trustees – comprising 11 members with a broad range of skills and
experience – is responsible for the overall control and strategic direction of
To help us achieve our vision for a word where diabetes can do no harm, we
benefit enormously from the work of a number of advisory groups:
* The Council of People Living with Diabetes (CPD) with between 20 and 25 members
* The Council of Healthcare Professionals (CHP) with up to 20 members
* National Advisory Councils in Scotland, Wales and Northern Ireland
Please contact our Governance Team if you would like any further information,
